#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.14"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.14:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.14:0.2"
msgid "2. Sāraṇīyavagga"
msgstr "2. Warm-hearted"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.14:0.3"
msgid "14. Bhaddakasutta"
msgstr "14. A Good Death"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.293"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.14:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There Sāriputta addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "an6.14:1.2"
msgid "“āvuso bhikkhave”ti."
msgstr "“Reverends, mendicants!”"

msgctxt "an6.14:1.3"
msgid "“Āvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato sāriputtassa paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Reverend,” they replied."

msgctxt "an6.14:1.4"
msgid "Āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca:"
msgstr "Sāriputta said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: kālakiriyā → kālaṃkiriyā (mr)
msgctxt "an6.14:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Tathā tathā, āvuso, bhikkhu vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ "
"kappayato na bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, na bhaddikā kālakiriyā."
msgstr "“A mendicant lives life so as to not have a good death."

msgctxt "an6.14:2.2"
msgid ""
"Kathañcāvuso, bhikkhu tathā tathā vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ "
"kappayato na bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, na bhaddikā kālakiriyā?"
msgstr "And how do they live life so as to not have a good death?"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an6.14:3.1"
msgid ""
"Idhāvuso, bhikkhu kammārāmo hoti kammarato kammārāmataṃ anuyutto, bhassārāmo "
"hoti bhassarato bhassārāmataṃ anuyutto, niddārāmo hoti niddārato "
"niddārāmataṃ anuyutto, saṅgaṇikārāmo hoti saṅgaṇikarato saṅgaṇikārāmataṃ "
"anuyutto, saṃsaggārāmo hoti saṃsaggarato saṃsaggārāmataṃ anuyutto, "
"papañcārāmo hoti papañcarato papañcārāmataṃ anuyutto."
msgstr ""
"Take a mendicant who relishes work, talk, sleep, company, closeness, and "
"proliferation. They love these things and like to relish them."

msgctxt "an6.14:3.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, āvuso, bhikkhu tathā tathā vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ "
"kappayato na bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, na bhaddikā kālakiriyā."
msgstr "A mendicant who lives life like this does not have a good death."

msgctxt "an6.14:3.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccatāvuso:"
msgstr "This is called"

#. VAR: nappajahāsi → na pahāsi (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an6.14:3.4"
msgid ""
"‘bhikkhu sakkāyābhirato nappajahāsi sakkāyaṃ sammā dukkhassa antakiriyāya’."
msgstr ""
"a mendicant who enjoys identity, who hasn’t given up identity to rightly "
"make an end of suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an6.14:4.1"
msgid ""
"Tathā tathāvuso, bhikkhu vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ kappayato "
"bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, bhaddikā kālakiriyā."
msgstr "A mendicant lives life so as to have a good death."

msgctxt "an6.14:4.2"
msgid ""
"Kathañcāvuso, bhikkhu tathā tathā vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ "
"kappayato bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, bhaddikā kālakiriyā?"
msgstr "And how do they live life so as to have a good death?"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.294"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an6.14:5.1"
msgid ""
"Idhāvuso, bhikkhu na kammārāmo hoti na kammarato na kammārāmataṃ anuyutto, "
"na bhassārāmo hoti na bhassarato na bhassārāmataṃ anuyutto, na niddārāmo "
"hoti na niddārato na niddārāmataṃ anuyutto, na saṅgaṇikārāmo hoti na "
"saṅgaṇikarato na saṅgaṇikārāmataṃ anuyutto, na saṃsaggārāmo hoti na "
"saṃsaggarato na saṃsaggārāmataṃ anuyutto, na papañcārāmo hoti na papañcarato "
"na papañcārāmataṃ anuyutto."
msgstr ""
"Take a mendicant who doesn’t relish work, talk, sleep, company, closeness, "
"and proliferation. They don’t love these things or like to relish them."

msgctxt "an6.14:5.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, āvuso, bhikkhu tathā tathā vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ "
"kappayato bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, bhaddikā kālakiriyā."
msgstr "A mendicant who lives life like this has a good death."

msgctxt "an6.14:5.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccatāvuso:"
msgstr "This is called"

msgctxt "an6.14:5.4"
msgid ""
"‘bhikkhu nibbānābhirato pajahāsi sakkāyaṃ sammā dukkhassa antakiriyāyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"a mendicant who enjoys extinguishment, who has given up identity to rightly "
"make an end of suffering."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an6.14:6.1"
msgid "Yo papañcamanuyutto,"
msgstr "A creature who likes to proliferate,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.14:6.2"
msgid "papañcābhirato mago;"
msgstr "enjoying proliferation,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.14:6.3"
msgid "Virādhayī so nibbānaṃ,"
msgstr "fails to reach extinguishment,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.14:6.4"
msgid "yogakkhemaṃ anuttaraṃ."
msgstr "the supreme sanctuary."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an6.14:7.1"
msgid "Yo ca papañcaṃ hitvāna,"
msgstr "But one who gives up proliferation,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.14:7.2"
msgid "nippapañcapade rato;"
msgstr "enjoying the state of non-proliferation,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.14:7.3"
msgid "Ārādhayī so nibbānaṃ,"
msgstr "reaches extinguishment,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.14:7.4"
msgid "yogakkhemaṃ anuttaran”ti."
msgstr "the supreme sanctuary.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.14:7.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
